description:
Danny welcomes the wonderful Alyson Hannigan to the Everything Iconic to talk about her role on season 2 of Pure, plus they chat about her legendary career, including her roles in such iconic entertainment as Buffy the Vampire Slayer, How I Met Your Mother, the American Pie franchise, and so much more.

Follow Alyson on Instagram- @alysonhannigan & watch season 2 of PURE on WGN America.


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
